title: Venezuela 1-1 Argentina: Rondon equaliser thwarts world champions on Messi return
description: Argentina dropped points in a second successive CONMEBOL World Cup qualifier, as Venezuela held them to a 1-1 draw in Maturin. The spoils were shared at Estadio Monumental de Maturin, where Salomon Rondon’s second-half header cancelled out Nicolas Otamendi’s earlier effort. title: Israel 1-4 France: Rampant Bleus clinch back-to-back Nations League wins
